+
+## Content Guardrails (Normative)
+
+Scenario pages MUST comply with:
+
+- `growth/marketing_landing_recognition_first_v1_2.md`
+- `../../../design/copy/kinly/web/scenario_landing_copy_contract_v1.md`
+
+Scenario pages MUST NOT:
+
+- imply surveillance, coercion, punishment, or scoring
+- bypass region gating behavior
+- add additional capture forms beyond approved growth contracts
+
+## Tracking Guardrails (Normative)
+
+Scenario pages MUST emit outreach events using their configured `page_key`.
+
+Tracking behavior is governed by:
+
+- `growth/outreach_tracking_v1_1.md`
+
+## Region Gating Guardrails (Normative)
+
+Scenario pages MUST use the active supported-region allowlist from:
+
+- `../links/links_region_gate_v1_3.md`
+
+## Change Rules
+
+The following are behavioral changes and REQUIRE a new contract version:
+
+- adding/removing a scenario slug
+- changing a slug, entry alias, or page key
+- changing canonical route namespace
+- changing scenario safety boundaries
+
+## Non-Goals
+
+This contract does not define:
+
+- deep-link internals
+- app-side behavior
+- mobile onboarding logic
+- scenario copy wording line-by-line
